Interface SamlServiceProviderRegistration

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Auditable, Deletable, Resource, Saveable

    public interface SamlServiceProviderRegistration
extends Resource, Saveable, Deletable, Auditable
    A SamlServiceProviderRegistration represents the link between a SamlIdentityProvider and a RegisteredSamlServiceProvider
